            <event xml:id="e005"
               type="event">
               <head xml:lang="en">
                  <date notBefore="1969-05-28" notAfter="1969-05-28">1969-05-28</date>
               </head>
               <desc>
                  <title xml:lang="en">28 May 1969, Kirchstetten, Lower Austria</title>
                  Musulin introduces Auden and Kallman to the Austrian historian, journalist, and intellectual Friedrich Heer (1916-1983); in Auden and Kallman's guest book, she notes : "Tag einer historischen Begegnung! [Day of a historical encounter!]" <!-- reference to Typed Letter Stella Musulin [to Edith Silbermann] [1969-05-29] -->
                  <location>
                     <geo>48.18153367563077 15.811562798177427</geo>
                     <address>
