               </head>
               <desc>
                  <title xml:lang="en">1971, London</title>
                  Publication of Musulin's monograph <hi rend="italic">Austria: People and Landscape</hi>, including a foreword by Auden, with Faber and Faber; the book's American edition - once more including Auden's foreword - came out in 1972 with Praeger Publishers, entitled <hi rend="italic">Austria and the Austrians</hi>
